Field Label:
(Read script)

You have just finished the Movies, and next you will be doing the Robot task. It will take about 9 minutes.

You will pretend that you are time travelling to the future. You will meet a robot. It will be talking to you in its own language, but you are not going to be able to understand it. Your job is just to listen carefully to what the robot is saying.

Remember to keep your body and your head as still as possible.
